@NODE "Features" "Feature List"
@TOC "MAIN"

        NewUser has the following features :

        » Creation of a memo-letter about the new user
        » Creation of NewUser-info files
        » Creation of a NewUser list
        » Simple input usage
        » Forcing a precise input
        » Extra input options
        » Using databases of countries and cities
        » Modify lay-out colours
        » Small but nice lay-out
@ENDNODE

